Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.03,0:01:32.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,…蟑螂
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.98,0:01:38.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真一郎的腳底上也有蟑螂
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.18,0:01:44.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真一郎的帽子裡也有蟑螂
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.53,0:01:55.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真一郎的心底裡
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.04,0:01:57.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,湯淺比呂美
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.69,0:02:32.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,飛吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.39,0:02:39.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,飛吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.91,0:02:40.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快呀
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.38,0:02:58.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,住手
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.40,0:03:00.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.48,0:03:03.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然  還是不行
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.05,0:03:08.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果不自己來決定
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.27,0:03:14.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就不會快樂  不會高興  不會歡笑呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.23,0:03:24.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然不自己來決定
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.14,0:03:26.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就哭不出來呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.35,0:03:29.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,之所以看不起無法飛翔的你
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.89,0:03:32.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是因為我認為你和不能飛翔的我一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.59,0:03:33.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是不對
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.24,0:03:36.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為你選擇了不去飛翔
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.53,0:03:40.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,挺起胸膛  正視前方
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.63,0:03:44.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那便和飛翔是同樣的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.38,0:04:02.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  我想乃繪馬上就會回來的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.07,0:04:07.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不像是有發生過什麼事  放心吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.73,0:04:09.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也幫我把這話轉告給他
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.12,0:04:13.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒關係
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.14,0:04:14.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那再聯繫
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.03,0:04:22.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那傢伙在說什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.82,0:04:26.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把地面看作自己的是我
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.42,0:04:30.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒有察覺地面厲害之處的是我
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.27,0:04:35.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,逃避了面對現實的是我
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.82,0:04:43.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,地面選擇了不去飛翔
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.99,0:04:46.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我沒有自己作出任何一個抉擇
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.81,0:04:52.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,無論是舞蹈  連環畫  乃繪  還是比呂美
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.72,0:04:57.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不想去跳舞並不是因為跳不好
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.64,0:05:00.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而是不想被別人拿我和父親做比較！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.66,0:05:04.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不能畫好連環畫並不是因為不在狀態
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.44,0:05:07.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是害怕知道自己的能力極限
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.75,0:05:25.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呱呱
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.05,0:05:36.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呱呱  呱呱  呱呱…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.38,0:06:39.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,回來了啊  乃繪
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.20,0:06:42.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我回來了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.96,0:06:45.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快去洗手  馬上就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.25,0:06:48.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,肚子餓了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.72,0:06:49.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,整晚都…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.67,0:06:52.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂  別抱這麼緊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.96,0:06:53.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,飯要…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.95,0:06:54.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.39,0:06:58.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.38,0:07:00.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.58,0:07:09.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好冷好冷  趕快回去烤暖爐吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.99,0:07:13.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.56,0:07:16.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不好意思呀  老闆娘
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.64,0:07:17.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦？少爺呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.11,0:07:22.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,衣服早就換好了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.29,0:07:23.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.18,0:07:25.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我去看一下
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.25,0:07:28.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他是在你原來的房間裡做準備的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.57,0:07:30.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.82,0:07:32.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,幫他換衣服嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.48,0:07:33.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好羨慕呀
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.39,0:07:35.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好啦  好啦  別亂說
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.11,0:07:36.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喝一杯吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.14,0:07:36.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦  好的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.69,0:07:38.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,來啊  來啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.30,0:07:40.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喝就要喝本地名酒
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.57,0:07:43.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,三年連續獲得金獎的  淚參旨
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.57,0:07:45.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,芳醇得好似真的要流淚
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.13,0:08:11.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要我幫忙嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.67,0:08:17.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很合身啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.32,0:08:18.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.80,0:08:21.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真一郎君也是
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.27,0:08:24.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝選購淚參旨一瓶
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.08,0:08:27.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那之後有好好睡過嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.40,0:08:30.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  那個…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.47,0:08:36.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,昨晚嚇了一跳  就打了電話
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.23,0:08:37.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.13,0:08:38.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.14,0:08:41.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明明為了今天而一直在練習
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.67,0:08:43.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都說跟那事沒關係了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.83,0:08:45.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒睡好是因為  那個那個…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.50,0:08:48.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不用擔心我睡眠不足
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.23,0:08:49.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,反正我會興奮起來的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.30,0:08:54.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在哪裡看得更清楚呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.39,0:08:57.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,重頭戲的奉納舞
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.04,0:09:01.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想在最近的地方看真一郎君跳
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.85,0:09:04.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然還是神社事務所的附近？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.93,0:09:10.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,祭典的時候我會在第一排看真一郎跳舞的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.67,0:09:12.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是呀
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.05,0:09:13.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,弄好了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.96,0:09:15.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.52,0:09:18.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一定會很擁擠
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.64,0:09:20.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不用勉強去看的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.37,0:09:36.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,祭典  不去看
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.60,0:09:39.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是自己認真定下的事
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.09,0:09:46.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好  上了！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.25,0:10:20.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,借過  借過
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.67,0:10:22.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉  我遲到了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.44,0:10:25.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎呀  我們這無所謂的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.76,0:10:27.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,反正奉納舞跳完之前都很閒
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.59,0:10:31.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對不起  都讓你做
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.52,0:10:32.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小愛  好久不見
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.38,0:10:36.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哇！比呂美穿和服好合身
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.36,0:10:49.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是來看真一郎的嗎  女朋友嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.62,0:10:51.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他的女朋友是我
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.65,0:11:09.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是  對於我來說  不知道的太多了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.00,0:11:25.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,石動同學
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.87,0:11:38.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等一下
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.99,0:11:39.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,昨晚
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.06,0:11:44.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,昨晚你和真一郎君說什麼了？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.20,0:11:47.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真一郎君對我說了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.70,0:11:50.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說全部  全部都會處理好的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.58,0:11:56.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我一直都喜歡真一郎君
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.77,0:11:58.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真一郎君也一定對我…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.15,0:12:01.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.86,0:12:04.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道我所說的很自私
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.86,0:12:07.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是我們好不容易才能心意相通的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.37,0:12:10.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們好不容易才能坦誠相對的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.18,0:12:13.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以後…對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.56,0:12:14.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別再打擾我們了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.16,0:12:15.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.90,0:12:29.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很漂亮哦
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.19,0:12:32.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你的眼淚
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.76,0:12:59.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,肚子餓了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.40,0:13:02.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,少爺你要去哪？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.16,0:13:04.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  稍微離開下
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.01,0:13:07.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,給  久等啦
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.55,0:13:10.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小哥  剛才的那份還是半生不熟的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.42,0:13:13.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為使用香嫩無比的新鮮小麥粉
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.06,0:13:15.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,五分熟是正好的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.36,0:13:16.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你真會說話
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.65,0:13:18.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好  下一位客人
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.15,0:13:23.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為小愛去了文化館
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.92,0:13:25.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以這段時間我幫她看一下店
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.11,0:13:29.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,關係處得不錯啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.22,0:13:32.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,比起這個  你在幹什麼呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.94,0:13:33.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼幹什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.29,0:13:38.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是說麥端舞的當家花旦可以在這裡瞎轉悠嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.07,0:13:41.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.54,0:13:43.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我到底在做什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.40,0:13:52.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真一郎好吵
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.57,0:13:58.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真一郎的屁股裡也有蟑螂
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.08,0:14:22.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,乃繪
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.59,0:14:27.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,來電話了  是從東京的印刷公司打來的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.44,0:14:35.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老闆他們都去看祭典了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.92,0:14:38.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你可以暫時待在這裡
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.28,0:14:40.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼要自做主張？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.94,0:14:44.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你明明說要去專科學校的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.56,0:14:47.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼會突然就去工作
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.07,0:14:51.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,姥姥的外套…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.92,0:14:57.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,姥姥死後  有一段時間你把自己關在房間裡吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.15,0:14:59.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都不和朋友玩了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.35,0:15:03.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我覺得必須得保護你
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.50,0:15:05.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,永遠
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.10,0:15:08.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是我變得不太明白了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.37,0:15:13.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我只想著要保護你
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.63,0:15:16.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,連那些莫名其妙的事情都…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.55,0:15:18.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哥哥
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.26,0:15:22.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我  我很喜歡你
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.31,0:15:24.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也很喜歡純
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.58,0:15:27.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但比起你的喜歡來  大概…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.14,0:15:29.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我那是更加深刻一點的喜歡
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.87,0:15:34.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有這種感情也很奇怪
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.43,0:15:37.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以才向他拜託了那些事情
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.09,0:15:38.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.43,0:15:40.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不明白
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.88,0:15:43.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喜歡我就很奇怪？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.36,0:15:45.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有什麼不好的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.01,0:15:49.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可以吻你嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.73,0:15:53.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還小的時候也親過的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.99,0:16:00.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好的  但作為交換
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.29,0:16:03.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,工作的事你要重新考慮
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.18,0:16:23.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哥哥？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.18,0:16:33.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想要的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.52,0:16:36.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大概就是這樣的吻吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.24,0:16:40.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然我擅自定下了很多事
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.01,0:16:43.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過待在你的身邊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.12,0:16:46.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已經是一件很難受的事了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.10,0:17:06.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真一郎的心底裡…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.67,0:17:12.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的心底裡…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.32,0:17:16.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,連哥哥的心情也沒有察覺
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.77,0:17:19.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,連湯淺比呂美的心情也沒有察覺
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.55,0:17:25.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,連真一郎真正的心情也沒有察覺
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.68,0:17:35.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,從我空虛的瞳孔中
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.86,0:17:40.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的能流出眼淚嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.44,0:17:47.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今年的花旦一下子好很多了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.45,0:17:49.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個我記得是  仲上家的孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.04,0:17:51.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虎父無犬子
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.41,0:17:54.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是為什麼會一下子…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.32,0:18:23.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雷轟丸意識到的時候
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.23,0:18:25.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已經被紅果所引誘
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.96,0:18:27.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,站在了那土堤上
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.68,0:18:30.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想飛！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.27,0:18:33.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是因為吃了那紅果的緣故
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.98,0:18:36.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還是因為這白雪的緣故
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.34,0:18:38.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,無從知道
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.21,0:18:43.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是雷轟丸從心底裡發出這樣的想法
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.04,0:18:44.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.18,0:18:47.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想要畫連環畫是因為
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.71,0:18:53.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那眼神…一直堅信我能夠飛翔
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.51,0:19:02.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你想翱翔於天空
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.55,0:19:04.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是為了誰
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.40,0:19:06.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是為了榮譽和紀錄
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.92,0:19:10.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雷轟丸騰空而起
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.25,0:20:17.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,跳得真好呢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.98,0:20:19.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的呢  我都入神了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.00,0:20:30.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我看了  跳得真好
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.01,0:20:31.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.28,0:20:34.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,比呂美  我稍微…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.72,0:20:36.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在找石動同學嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.92,0:20:37.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.67,0:20:39.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我說出來了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.05,0:20:44.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,求石動同學  以後不要打擾我們了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.59,0:20:47.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,生氣了？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.27,0:20:49.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不  沒什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.11,0:20:53.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我…差不多得走了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.02,0:20:55.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,待會兒還有祭典的慶功宴
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.91,0:20:58.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要丟下我
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.14,0:21:06.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要丟下我
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.24,0:21:21.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,從天上眺望的感覺怎麼樣
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.65,0:21:25.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,連環畫
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.70,0:21:26.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,畫好了！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.56,0:21:29.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要是從天上向下看的話
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.79,0:21:31.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也能看得見嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.30,0:21:42.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我希望你看看
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.25,0:21:44.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想要知道你的感想
Dialogue: 0,0:23:41.07,0:23:42.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是嗎  謝謝
Dialogue: 0,0:23:44.65,0:23:45.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,進去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:23:46.55,0:23:48.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,討厭這樣的自己
Dialogue: 0,0:23:49.14,0:23:51.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真一郎說我能飛
Dialogue: 0,0:23:52.51,0:23:53.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把你的眼淚
